{"tid":1793603,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［重開］［人血饅頭］有條仆街扮星火律師籌錢","createTime":"2019-12-22T13:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:15:14.000Z","uid":110496,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25acf85395cb2052be6456b4fb4e76744f616e18","tid":1793603,"uid":110496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"話說小弟上一個post垃圾打漏咗個字，所以重開都<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意！有人發起眾籌，以「Kwok Tung Daniel Wong」名義，內文提及「黃國桐律師」及用了他的相片（下左右圖），但黃國桐律師已經澄清（上圖）「我地並無透過或有人接觸過我們，有關這個平台的籌款資訊，請相關平台發起人跟我們聯絡。」<br />\n<br />\n在黃國桐律師有進一步消息之前，請大家不要參與相關活動。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/「保護傘」計劃-助流亡台灣港人恢復正常生活\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E3%80%8C%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%82%98%E3%80%8D%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=46a9ee34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/「保護傘」計劃-助流亡台灣港人恢復正常生活</a><br />\n<br />\n黃國桐律師：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1031686794/posts/10215399193866338?d=n&amp;sfns=mohttps://www.facebook.com/692298914179660/posts/2581844935225039?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1031686794%2Fposts%2F10215399193866338%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmohttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F692298914179660%2Fposts%2F2581844935225039%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=647948e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1031686794/posts/10215399193866338?d=n&amp;sfns=mohttps://www.facebook.com/692298914179660/posts/2581844935225039?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHFcAGT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHFcAGT.png&h=c82394ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要小心，唔好見到錢就即刻捐，即使有當事人認證都睇定啲先<i